headline: Hartford (HIG): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q2 Earnings?
summary: Even though Hartford (currently trading at $133.39 per share) has gained 7.2% over the last six months, it has lagged the S&P 500’s 18.8% return during that period. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
